OL,3,CMan convicted of Stranraer murder
OL,5,FA man has been convicted of murdering
OL,6,Fa 33-year-old man in Stranraer at the
OL,7,FHigh Court in Glasgow.
OL,9,FMark Allison, 25, was found guilty of
OL,10,Fmurdering Gary Handling in the town.
OL,12,FMr Handling was injured on John
OL,13,FSimpson Drive on Monday 6 June, 2022.
OL,14,FHe was subsequently taken to Galloway
OL,15,FCommunity Hospital where he died a
OL,16,Fshort time later.
OL,18,FMr Allison is due to be sentenced on 5
OL,19,FMarch 2024.
