OL,5,FSenior Investigating Officer,
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Graeme Robertson,
OL,7,FDumfries and Galloway Division CID,
OL,8,Fsaid: "Our thoughts remain with Gary's
OL,9,Ffamily and friends at this difficult
OL,10,Ftime.
OL,12,F"This conviction shows that we will
OL,13,Fuse all the tools we have to
OL,14,Finvestigate and bring people who are
OL,15,Fintent on committing crime and harm to
OL,16,Fjustice.
OL,18,F"Allison will now have to face the
OL,19,Fconsequences of his actions.
